* Living Rooms as Factories: Class, Gender, and the Satellite Factory System in Taiwan (Temple University Press, 1996)；
* Chinese Women Organizing: Cadres, Feminists, Muslims, Queers (Berg, Oxford International Publishers, 2001, co-edited with Maria Jaschok and Cecilia Milwertz);

* “质性研究方法刍议：来自社会性别视角的探索 ,” 社会学研究，95期：17-34, 2001； 
*“Teaching Reflexivity in Qualitative Interviewing,”Teaching Sociology, 36 (July): 211-226, 2008; 
* 客厅即工厂，熊秉纯著；蔡一平、张玉萍、刘子剑译；重庆大学出版社2010；
*“深度访谈中‘反思’的教与学，”质性研究：反思与评论， 2:3-24, 2010;
* Lives and Legacies: A Guide to Qualitative Interviewing (2010)

